## 硬性目标 (不可放弃, 按 R4)

`AllreduceSdma(copy_output_to_user=True)(input, output, stream)` 的 multi-stage overlap wall **≤ RCCL `dist.all_reduce(tensor)` wall**.

测量: 256MB / stage × 4 stages × 8-rank MI355X, `tests/python/ccl/test_allreduce.py --num-stages 4 --elems 67108864 --iterations 100 --warmup 20`, median over ≥100 iters.

---

## 当前性能数据 (2026-04-28, HEAD=`611c2f2c`, Plan A 实测 FAILED)

### Plan A 实测 (Entry 20)

| 变体 | overlap wall | seq_ar | seq_gemm | overlap/seq_gemm | vs RCCL |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| **Plan A (SDMA copy + DIRECT_OUTPUT=1)** | **9.084 ms** | 5.845 | 4.129 | 2.200 | **+21.1% (+1.58ms WORSE)** |
| SDMA no-copy | 7.355 ms | 4.801 | 3.991 | 1.843 | -2.0% |
| RCCL today | 7.503 ms | 5.133 | 3.977 | 1.887 | — |

vs Entry 19 BASELINE 7.802 ms: **Plan A 慢 1.28 ms**.

### Plan A 失败的根因 (机制层面, 不是 implementation bug)

**架构错配**: Plan A 把 AG 从独立 SDMA engine 搬到 CU. 在 GEMM overlap 场景下, Plan A 的 AR 阶段和 GEMM 抢 CU.

**机制 1 (seq_ar +0.66ms)**: BASELINE 用 SDMA AG, CU 在 chunk c+1 reduce 时 SDMA 同时做 chunk c AG (chunk pipeline depth 2). Plan A CU AG 占 CU, chunk c+1 reduce 必须等 chunk c AG pull 完成 (depth 1).

**机制 2 (overlap +1.28ms)**: per-AR CU 占用越多, GEMM overlap 退化越严重. 单调关系 (4 个数据点验证):

| algorithm | per-AR CU 占用 | overlap/seq_gemm |
|---|---|---|
| RCCL ring (sparse) | ~14 × 0.05 ms 间歇 | **1.89** (最低) |
| BASELINE (SDMA AG) | reduce only ~0.30 ms | **2.12** |
| **Plan A** (CU pull AG + write) | reduce + barrier + pull + write ~1.0 ms | **2.20** |
| Plan B (CU push + CU copy) | reduce + push + copy ~0.95 ms | **2.44** (最高) |

**结论**: 任何把 AG/copy 移到 CU 的方案在 GEMM overlap 场景都失败 (CU 是 GEMM 的主要硬件, SDMA engine 是 GEMM 不用的"免费"硬件). Plan A + Plan B 双重验证. **无任何 vectorize / partition / CU 数 调整能补 1.58ms gap**, 是 architectural decision 错误.

---

## 根因 (一句话)

SDMA two-shot 算法比 RCCL 多一步 **256MB transit → user_output copy** (外部 `hipMemcpyAsync` CU blit, 每 AR ~0.35 ms, 4 AR × 0.35 = 1.4 ms), 这是 **唯一** 的 gap. SDMA no-copy wall 6.93 ms 已超 RCCL 0.5 ms (Entry 16).

---

## 已验证 FAILED 的方向 (不得重试, 除非有新机制证据)

| 方向 | Entry | 失败原因 |
|---|---|---|
| τ (MORI_KEEP_HBM_HOT) | 14 | HBM hot keep 对 AG 无加速 |
| ξ (MORI_AR_WARMUP) | 14 | pre-warm 对 cold path 无加速 |
| ν (MORI_SKIP_ITER_SYNC) | 15 | 测量 artifact, 非真实 gain |
| τ'' (MORI_HBM_NOISE) | 16 | HBM noise 对 AG 无影响 |
| E'' (MORI_INKERNEL_COPY) | 17 | compute block 在 AG wait 时 copy → HBM 争用 |
| D' (shmem register user_output, 自动) | 11 | PyTorch caching allocator + `hipIpcOpenMemHandle` offset 语义冲突 → correctness fail |
| **Plan B** (K1 SDMA scatter + K2 CU reduce+**push**AG+CU copy) | **18** | CU AG + GEMM 抢 CU. wall +1.16 ms 退化. overlap/seq_gemm 2.44 |
| **Plan A** (K1 SDMA scatter + K2 CU reduce+**pull**AG+ 直写 user_output) | **20** | 同 Plan B 机制: CU AG + GEMM 抢 CU. wall **+1.58 ms vs RCCL** (+21.1% WORSE). overlap/seq_gemm 2.20. **架构错误,任何实现优化补不齐** |
| CU sweep (80..220) | 3 | copy exposure 在 CU ≥120 下 invariant |
| 压 kernel priority | 5 | priority 对 wall 无 measurable effect |

**关键教训** (R6, 数据驱动):
- **CU-as-AG 在 GEMM overlap 场景下 fundamentally 失败** (Plan A + Plan B 双重验证 — 同机制).
- 单调关系: per-AR CU 占用 ↔ overlap/seq_gemm ratio. 实测 4 个数据点 (RCCL 1.89 < BASELINE 2.12 < Plan A 2.20 < Plan B 2.44). 占 CU 越多 overlap 退化越大.
- 任何未来涉及 "用 CU 替代 SDMA 做 AG 或 copy" 的方案 (e.g., CU XGMI pull/push, CU memcpy, in-kernel transit copy) 应**直接拒绝**, 不需再 bench. 已有数据点足够预测.
- 唯一可走方向: **保留 SDMA AG**, 优化或消除 transit→user_output copy.

